{"tid":2514015,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"52歲社署院舍女服務員叫罵黑警兼拒捕早前被判囚10周 今放棄上訴即時服刑","createTime":"2021-05-03T03:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T10:43:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a4917645812ba508fafefb382eee2079a801380e","tid":2514015,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"社署院舍女服務員前年11月12日晚上身穿街坊裝束，被指在街頭叫罵「黑警」，引起別人叫囂，又推撞扯她口罩的防暴男警胸口，被控非法集結、拒捕及違反蒙面法三罪，早前經審訊後被裁定三罪全部成立，判監10個星期。她早前獲准保釋等候上訴，惟她今在高等法院庭上確認放棄上訴，須即時服刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/O66C24D5JFHOJENUTYEQAP7DI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FO66C24D5JFHOJENUTYEQAP7DI4%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOHRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=df0c18a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FO66C24D5JFHOJENUTYEQAP7DI4%2F&h=22a177a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/O66C24D5JFHOJENUTYEQAP7DI4/</a>"},{"pid":"c2ff56337cd66f1e7ca17c1819039098392fbb6e","tid":2514015,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15384&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOHRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=0d8099fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15384</a><br />\n<br />\n#高等法院第廿二庭<br />\n#張慧玲法官<br />\n#1112天水圍 #不服定罪上訴<br />\n#拒捕 #非法集結 #蒙面法<br />\n<br />\n蔡(50) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 參與非法集結<br />\n被控於19年11月12日於天水圍天湖路與天耀路交界，與其他不知名人士參與非法集結<br />\n<br />\n(2) 抗拒在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n被控於同日同地抗拒警長9486<br />\n<br />\n(3) 在身處非法集結時使用蒙面物品<br />\n被控於同日同地身處非法集結時，使用相當可能阻止識別身份的蒙面物品即 一個掛耳口罩<br />\n<br />\n經審訊，#王證瑜裁判官 於20年11月23日裁定被告罪名全部成立，判處總刑期10星期監禁，上訴期間申請保釋獲批。裁決原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11502&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOHRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=cf4b78c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11502</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n【速報】<br />\n🛑蔡手足於21年4月21日放棄所有控罪上訴，並即時服刑<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"eb27af628a6cb365291c3b8ac6db2662882f9947","tid":2514015,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec7af6cc74d0e1f7f4e1b3324af106664a15c02","tid":2514015,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:47:42.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f48a41cf4828fc0ad840ef3b43efc57664ef40","tid":2514015,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdbcd6139a492062e2997b6fa6e1c76d0eaaa47","tid":2514015,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:03:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"099b2c43898fe4e617adb5529b70233fc021807c","tid":2514015,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:51:17.000Z","msg":"點解要認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc1b78413091e60e15dc18643392fa1eca92689","tid":2514015,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414d45b4fffbaed87cd653829c0eac09d2bc67ea","tid":2514015,"uid":49685,